race.comment: Open race to close out the card. MARGOT BARBIE (5) has a solid record over this track and trip with a win and five placings from ten starts and will strip fitter third-up from the break. Expecting sharp improvement in this contest. VEGAMEISTER (7) boasts a win over this course and distance and is better than the past couple of efforts suggest. Worth another chance. MISTER DOOBEE (10) shed the maiden tag last time out and will have taken some confidence from that victory. Looks the runner in this field with the most upside. The well-related COPPABELLA ROAD (1) (half to Listed winner and G3 placed Catoggio) is one from one when racing second-up and can feature without surprising. STATESWOMAN (8) next in line.
